snippet.title: Those Nights at Rachel's | Gameplay Trailer
snippet.description:
Those Nights at Rachel's | Gameplay Trailer

Trailer for my Five Nights at Freddy's Fan Game "Those Nights at Rachel's"

The game is heavily inspired by FNaF, but there are NO characters from the franchise(well, kinda) , the setting and animatronics are custom, however it takes place in the same universe!

You can follow the game here! http://gamejolt.com/games/those-nights-at-rachel-s/114026
